article_id:3203,category_name:News,title_name:A Platinum Showcase Is Now Live! Light-Attuned 5★ Adventurer Guaranteed!,image_path:,message:<div>A Platinum Showcase started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1668751200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a light-attuned 5★ adventurer is guaranteed to appear.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include adventurers and dragons that are attuned to elements other than light.</span></div><div><br></div><div>During the period, players are limited to doing the Platinum Showcase summon two times, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1668751200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1669787999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the light-attuned 5★ adventurers eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5★ summon below.</div><div><br></div><div>
